og_description: Explore highlights of the various Air Force Specialty Codes in the 192nd Wing, Virginia Air National Guard. The wing is headquartered at Joint Base Langley-Eustis, Virginia. In addition to state missions, the wing associates with the regular Air Force, spanning three major commands, and performs standalone federal missions. (U.S. Air National Guard video by Staff Sgt.
